data.description: Welcome to your dream single-story home with no HOA! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property has been beautifully renovated with new floors, remodeled bathrooms, and updated kitchen cabinets with all new stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the comfort of a newer water heater and windows throughout the home. The open floor plan makes this home perfect for entertaining, and there's plenty of potential for you to make it your own. The large front driveway provides ample parking space for you and your guests. Located in a desirable neighborhood just minutes away from Summerlin's shopping, dining, and entertainment, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home!
